longBusinessSummary: Embassy Developments Limited operates as a real estate company in India. The company engages in the provision of real estate properties advisory, properties marketing, engineering, industrial, and technical consultancy services; maintenance of completed properties; construction and development of real estate properties; and other ancillary services. Its project portfolio includes residential and commercial, as well as SEZ projects. The company was formerly known as Equinox India Developments Limited and changed its name to Embassy Developments Limited in February 2025. Equinox India Developments Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Mumbai, India.
